file.name: osticket.yaml
file.content:
components:
  schemas:
    tmp0:
      properties:
        id: {type: string}
      type: object
  securitySchemes: {}
info:
  contact: {email: frikky@shuffler.io, name: '@frikkylikeme', url: 'https://twitter.com/frikkylikeme'}
  description: Automated generation of Enhancesoft OSTicket
  title: Enhancesoft OSTicket
  version: 1.0.0
  x-logo: data:image/png;base64,
openapi: 3.0.2
paths:
  tmp0:
    post:
      description: Create a new ticket on OSTicket
      parameters:
      - description: Email address of the submitter
        example: api@osticket.com
        in: query
        name: Email
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Name of the submitter
        example: Angry User
        in: query
        name: Name
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Subject of the ticket
        example: Testing API
        in: query
        name: Subject
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Initial message for the ticket thread
        example: This is a message
        in: query
        name: Message
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: If unset, disable alerts to staff
        example: ''
        in: query
        name: Alert
        required: false
        schema: {type: boolean}
      - description: If unset, disable autoresponses
        example: ''
        in: query
        name: Autorespond
        required: false
        schema: {type: boolean}
      - description: IP address of the submitter
        example: 123.211.233.122
        in: query
        name: IP
        required: false
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Priority id for the new ticket to assume
        example: ''
        in: query
        name: Priority
        required: false
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Source of the ticket
        example: API
        in: query
        name: Source
        required: false
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Help topic id associated with the ticket
        example: ''
        in: query
        name: Topic ID
        required: false
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: An array of files to attach to the initial message
        example: ''
        in: query
        name: Attachments
        required: false
        schema: {type: string}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp0'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: OSTicket Create Ticket
tags:
- {name: Ticket Management}
